                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to a conviction for burglary at this Court on 1st February</hi>, 1875, <hi rend="italic">and another was proved against him—<rs id="t18751122-45-punishment-45" type="punishmentDescription">
